While the technical innovation is minimal, the business impact is notable due to the clear pricing strategy and potential revenue streams.

changes.title: Comparing Midjourney Plans – Midjourney
changes.content_preview:
Title: Comparing Midjourney Plans – Midjourney

Skip to main content
Midjourney
Midjourney
 Billing Support
 Plan Information
Comparing Midjourney Plans
All Midjourney plans are subscriptions - meaning they automatically renew on a monthly or yearly basis unless you set your plan to cancel.

Midjourney offers four subscription tiers: Basic, Standard, Pro, and Mega. See the chart below for a comparison of plan features.

For unlimited image generations with Relax Mode, subscribe to the Standard, Pro, or Mega Plan.
For unlimited video generations with Relax Mode, subscribe to the Pro or Mega Plan. 
Stealth Mode, which keeps your images and videos private, is only available on the Pro and Mega Plans.

You can get a 20% discount on your subscription by committing to an annual plan, where the full year fee is paid upfront.

 	Basic Plan	Standard Plan	Pro Plan	Mega Plan
Monthly Price	$10	$30	$60	$120
Annual Price	$96
($8 / month)	$288
($24 / month)	$576
($48 / month)	$1,152
($96 / month)
